# Twizted Metal ZK DeFi League

## Overview

- Tournaments & Leagues with anonymous registration (ZK)
- DeFi integration: borrow/lend with Fluid/Solend
- SOL staking/wagering for matches

## Structure

- `anchor/` — Solana Anchor contracts
- `circom/` — ZK circuits
- `frontend/` — React frontend

## Getting Started

1. **Anchor**
    - Install [Anchor](https://project-serum.github.io/anchor/getting-started/installation.html)
    - `cd anchor && anchor build`
2. **Circom**
    - Install [Circom](https://docs.circom.io/getting-started/installation/)
    - Compile circuits: `circom identity.circom --r1cs --wasm --sym`
3. **Frontend**
    - `cd frontend && npm install`
    - `npm run dev` or deploy to GitHub Pages

